Backend :

Technologies:
•Python
•Flask
•Pandas
•Scikit-learn
•NLTK
•NumPy

Backend Functions :
•Receive news text from frontend.
•Clean and preprocess the text.
•Convert text using TF-IDF.
•Send text to the trained machine learning     model.
•Predict whether the news is fake or real.
•Return the result to the frontend.

